name: regen_sed_notification_name
subject: GenAI Entitlement Descriptions Have Been Regenerated
body:
Dear $__recipient.name,

Based on your GenAI Settings input, ${SedRegenerationCount} entitlement descriptions have been regenerated to more accurately reflect your context. You can review the regenerated descriptions on the GenAI Entitlement Descriptions page.


Thanks,
The $__global.productName Team
